    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=cwqx4zd13l]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=cwqx4zd13l]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=nk0k76h0ba]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=nk0k76h0ba]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=pyk3inuxpd]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=pyk3inuxpd]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=n63g625klx]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=n63g625klx]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong><span data-colorid=\"n63g625klx\">Resource</span></strong>: HDRI</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"pyk3inuxpd\">Library Created By</span></strong>: Dylan Sisson</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"nk0k76h0ba\">Updated by</span></strong>: Leif Pedersen</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"cwqx4zd13l\">Use</span></strong>: Attach to RenderMan PxrDomeLight</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://assets.renderman.pixar.com/resources/stylized_env_lights/9392_stylized_hdri_v21.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469173/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285533717&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=47\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608469173/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285533717&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608469209\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608469173\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"0f2e7709-b362-44ae-b72a-89b6aa494354\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469173/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285533717&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469173/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285533717&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=47 1x\" /></span></a><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><h1 id=\"StylizedLights-Overview\">Overview</h1><p>With this Stylized Environment Light Library, you'll be able to use some realistic, psychedelic, and stylized HDRI with RenderMan's Preset Browser.</p><p><br />Enjoy!</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"9398_stylized_hdri.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469173/9398_stylized_hdri.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285632643&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=712\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608469173/9398_stylized_hdri.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285632643&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"960\" data-width=\"1024\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"607846749\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"9398_stylized_hdri.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608469173\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"8c9e7152-8a43-4258-b026-6eb32f6304db\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469173/9398_stylized_hdri.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285632643&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1024&amp;height=960 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469173/9398_stylized_hdri.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285632643&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=712 1x\" /></span><h2 id=\"StylizedLights-How-to\">How-to</h2><p>Place the <strong>Stylized</strong> folder inside your RenderMan Asset Library <strong>EnvironmentMaps</strong> folder. It is recommended that you transfer the installation default RenderManAssetLibrary folder to a non-install location with full writing privileges.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"9369_stylized_env_lights.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469173/9369_stylized_env_lights.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285649724&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=286\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608469173/9369_stylized_env_lights.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285649724&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"381\" data-width=\"1009\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"607912357\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"9369_stylized_env_lights.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608469173\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ea6545af-85bb-44b1-bb24-a8b723b61bdf\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469173/9369_stylized_env_lights.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285649724&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1009&amp;height=381 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469173/9369_stylized_env_lights.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285649724&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=286 1x\" /></span><p>Once you transfer the Materials folder and move your Asset Library into a different location, it is essential to tell Maya through the preferences that you want to use the new path.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"preset-browser-add-library.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469173/preset-browser-add-library.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285533046&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=609\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608469173/preset-browser-add-library.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285533046&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"622\" data-width=\"776\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608469185\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"preset-browser-add-library.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608469173\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"99cd7a31-b7a6-4681-a08b-703bca0b5804\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469173/preset-browser-add-library.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285533046&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=776&amp;height=622 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469173/preset-browser-add-library.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285533046&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=609 1x\" /></span><p>Your preset browser will show all new presets, including our new <strong>Stylized</strong> Env Lights&mdash;no need to restart Maya. You might need to close and open the Preset Browser to refresh.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"9391_stylized_env_lights_preset_browser.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469173/9391_stylized_env_lights_preset_browser.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285669331&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=286\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608469173/9391_stylized_env_lights_preset_browser.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285669331&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"381\" data-width=\"1009\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"607945068\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"9391_stylized_env_lights_preset_browser.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608469173\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"55d9eed5-1257-4d55-9ffd-7a0768353f3d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469173/9391_stylized_env_lights_preset_browser.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285669331&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1009&amp;height=381 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469173/9391_stylized_env_lights_preset_browser.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285669331&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=286 1x\" /></span><p /><hr /><h3 id=\"StylizedLights-Copyright\">Copyright</h3><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/mark/1.0/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Public Domain. Free of known copyright restrictions.</a></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"cc-zero.png\" width=\"127\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469173/cc-zero.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285533717&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=127&amp;height=44\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608469173/cc-zero.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285533717&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"142\" data-width=\"403\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608469206\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"cc-zero.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608469173\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c54eb065-ee96-48c8-90a7-e7013c0a9d00\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469173/cc-zero.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285533717&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=254&amp;height=88 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469173/cc-zero.png?v